<br>
1.  long respawn on quest NPC<br>
2.  akheva pieces are no rent and not attainable solo (unless you get lucky and some group lets you sit around and loot them)<br>
3.  need a rogue to open the door<br>
4.  piqi has realtively long spawn time.<br>
<br>
<br>
so 2 cloaks per day can come into the game max.  60 cloaks a month isn't bad.  and anyone wanting to start the quest will hav to get the quest before someone turns in the items....so more like 30-45 a month i'd say.<br>
<br>
for comparison, when velious came out, chief rygorr was camped 24/7.  he's a 1 hour spawn, so that's 24 possible drops a day.  when you factor in spears and no drops, you're talking about 10-18 tunics a day (300-540 a month). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
